data.description:
This freshly renovated home for rent in Mount Holly, NJ is a must see!! Spacious, bright, and airy, with new flooring and fresh paint throughout. Four large bedrooms provide plenty of room for growing family. Kitchen is sunny and bright with open layout. Appliances included- oven/stove, fridge/freezer, washer/dryer. Large, semi-finished basement with ideal room for office or other purposes. Located in quiet, family friendly neighborhood. Large yard and full driveway. Just a short drive to shopping, dining, schools and other amenities. Pets are open for discussion. Come check out your next home! Serious inquiries only.

No smoking allowed. We are open to the option of pets- please call to discuss. Security deposit is one and half months of rent, refundable at end of lease provided all terms are met. Landlord will address any pest issues. Tenant is responsible for yard maintenance. Option of adding window A/C units. Tenant pays for all utilities including gas, electric and water.
